        "timestamp": "2019-01-05 00:01:56.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nthis does not fix the problem in SO-1358.\nI see the '\"' getting escaped in the catalog DB if I look directly with sql,\nbut what gets returned from the query has not escape and the json parsing still fails.\n\nI will post more details in the JIRA",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
