        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-05 20:53:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThank you Eric for helping me to test this patch.\n\nThe reason I found the escape character is not preserved because \n`matcher.appendReplacement()` handles `/` and `$` differently as special character. So I added following line to fix it:\ne.g.\nm.appendReplacement(result, Matcher.quoteReplacement(valueMap.getOrDefault(key, \"\\\"TBD\\\"\")))\n\nI confirmed the response using `CatalogDBRestTest.testGetServiceModelUUID()` test case.\n\nThe json response is not valid.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
